     2| * IVX Block 26 — Agent Self-Execution Test.
     3| *
     4| * The multi-agent framework autonomously assigns and completes one real
     5| * low-risk technical task end-to-end:
     6| *   CTO Orchestrator routes  ->  specialist accepts  ->  inspects file
     7| *   ->  records a safe proposal  ->  validates  ->  writes memory
